refillPaper() - Method in class uk.ac.westminster.ihanlelwala.printingsystem.LaserPrinter
method to refill paper tray of printer with paper paper tray can only be refilled if the new paper level does not exceed the full (maximum) paper level specified in ServicePrinter.FULL_PAPER_TRAY each paper refill increases the paper level by the number of papers in pack specified in ServicePrinter.SHEETS_PER_PACK

replaceTonerCartridge() - Method in class uk.ac.westminster.ihanlelwala.printingsystem.LaserPrinter
method to replace Toner cartridge of printer toner can only be replaced when current toner level goes below the minimum toner level specified in ServicePrinter.MINIMUM_TONER_LEVEL when toner cartridge is replaced, toner level goes upto full toner level specified in ServicePrinter.FULL_TONER_LEVEL
